headline: Is Lockheed Martin’s Recent Rise Justified After Pentagon Missile Production Push?
summary: Thinking about what to do with Lockheed Martin stock right now? You are definitely not alone. The price has turned some heads lately, especially with a 12.3% climb over the past month and a solid 3.5% gain in just the last week. Yet, when you zoom out a bit, the picture gets more nuanced, with a 14.3% drop over the past year. Longer-term investors are still up nearly 50% over five years. All of this sets the stage for an interesting question: is the recent bounce the start of a new chapter or...
